        "action": "Make Mondays part of the school weekend",
        "additional_details": "",
        "background": "I believe that weekends do not feel satisfactory finishing on Sundays as they feel too short. So, I propose, Weekend Monday. This could help take away the stress of Mondays and also allows students to be better rested for the coming school week, allowing for better focus and information detainment.",
